0of%20accounts%20to%20get%20more%20from%20their%20money%2C%20and%20they're%20hidden%20in%20plain%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERich%20people%20use%20Roth%20IRAs%20for%20tax%20advantages%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERich%20people%20are%20always%20looking%20to%20minimize%20the%20impact%20of%20taxes%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-roth-ira-accounts%5C%22%3ERoth%20IRA%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20designed%20to%20do%20just%20that.%20In%202021%2C%20PayPal%20founder%20Peter%20Thiel's%20Roth%20IRA%20account%20garnered%20attention%20for%20the%20strategy%20he%20used%20to%20grow%20the%20account%20from%20%241%2C700%20to%20%245%20billion%2C%20which%20he%20will%20eventually%20be%20able%20to%20withdraw%20completely%20tax-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoth%20IRAs%20minimize%20your%20tax%20bill%20later%20by%20only%20allowing%20deposits%20of%20money%20that%20have%20been%20made%20after%20taxes.%20While%20a%20Roth%20IRA%20won't%20lower%20your%20tax%20bill%20now%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Froth-vs-traditional-ira%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20IRA%3C%2Fa%3E%20does%2C%20a%20Roth%20IRA%20will%20allow%20the%20money%20to%20come%20out%20tax-free%20after%20it%20grows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoth%20IRAs%20do%20have%20income%20limits%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20wealthy%20people%20and%20high%20earners%20don't%20use%20them.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbackdoor-roth-ira%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebackdoor%20Roth%20IRA%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20turn%20a%20traditional%20IRA%20into%20an%20account%20with%20the%20tax%20benefits%20of%20a%20Roth%20IRA%2C%20transferring%20the%20funds%20from%20one%20type%20of%20account%20to%20another.%20While%20there%20may%20be%20taxes%20involved%20on%20any%20growth%20as%20you%20transfer%20the%20accounts%2C%20this%20method%20offers%20the