dardized-testing-back-ivy-league-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20lifelong%20Jersey%20girl%20choosing%20to%20retire%20in%20South%20Carolina.%20It's%20where%20my%20adult%20daughter%20is%20planning%20to%20live%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20cheaper.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20people%20walking%20down%20the%20street%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina%2C%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66184b921caec1275a6f58cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharleston%2C%20South%20Carolina.%3Cp%3EGlowimages%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKathie%20Zucker%2C%2057%2C%20lived%20in%20New%20Jersey%20her%20whole%20life%2C%20but%20is%20now%20moving%20to%20South%20Carolina.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20visiting%20her%20daughter%20%E2%80%94%20who%20attends%20college%20in%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina%2C%20she%20found%20that%20she%20liked%20the%20area.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20especially%20enjoys%20the%20warmer%20weather%2C%20activities%2C%20and%20cheaper%20cost%20of%20living%20around%20Charleston.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Kathie%20Zucker%2C%2057%2C%20and%20her%20decision%20to%20move%20to%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina%2C%20from%20the%20New%20York%20City%20suburb%20of%20Butler%2C%20New%20Jersey.%20The%20conversation%20was%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20to%20seriously%20look%20to%20move%20to%20Charleston%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20that%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20would%20talk%20about%20it%20and%20drive%20to%20different%20areas.%20Then%20we%20figured%20out%20areas%20we%20liked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20hard%20decision%20to%20make.%20You%20just%20say%20to%20yourself%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20husband%20and%20I%20are%20entering%20the%20second%20phase%20and%20moving%20toward%20retirement%20eventually.%20I'm%20an%20insurance%20agency%20manager.%20I'm%20too%20young%20to%20retire%20right%20now%2C%20but%20is%20New%20Jersey%20where%20I%20want%20to%20eventually%20be%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20answer%20was%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20that%20was%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20New%20Jersey.%20The%20property%20tax%20situation%20when%20you%20retire%20is%20still%20significant.%20I%20mean%2C%20you're%20talking%20%249%2C000%20a%20year%20%E2%80%94%20just%20increase%20after%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20to%20Charleston%20extensively%20to%20stay%20with%20my%20daughter.%20She%20transferred%20there%20from%20another%20school%20in%20Virginia.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20really%20on%20my%20radar%20as%20a%20place%20to%20retire%20%E2%80%94%20more%20so%20Florida%2C%20or%20somewhere%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20more%20I%20went%20to%20visit%20her%20and%20the%20more%20I%20saw%20of%20what%20it%20offered%2C%20the%20more%20I%20could%20visualize%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20retiring%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20consider%20Florida%2C%20but%20we%20ruled%20it%20out.%20For%20maybe%20a%20quick%20minute%20we%20considered%20North%20Carolina%20and%20ruled%20that%20out.%20But%20we%20definitely%20wanted%20something%20on%20the%20seaboard%20here%20in%20the%20east.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20wanted%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20my%20daughter%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20beach%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20had%20vacationed%20in%20Isle%20of%20Palms%2C%20which%20is%20near%20Charleston%2C%20for%20many%20years.%20But%20until%20my%20daughter%20went%20to%20school%20there%2C%20I%20never%20really%20went%20down%20and%20experienced%20it.%20It's%20funny%20that's%20where%20I%20ended%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wouldn't%20say%20my%20daughter%20living%20there%20was%20the%20sole%20consideration%20for%20moving.%20Out%20of%2010%2C%20I%20would%20probably%20have%20to%20say%20it's%20a%20seven.%20Wanting%20to%20be%20near%20your%20adult%20children%20was%20important%20for%20me%20and%20my%20husband%20because%20she's%20our%20only%20child.%20But%20then%20I%20think%20if%20she%20was%20in%20a%20place%20we%20definitely%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20she%20was%20in%20Virginia%2C%20where%20she%20originally%20started%20school%2C%20we%20probably%20would%20have%20looked%20in%20that%20area.%20But%20if%20she%20was%20in%20Ohio%2C%20there's%20not%20a%20chance%20I'd%20go%20to%20Ohio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20loves%20it%20down%20there%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20great%20place%20for%20her%20to%20call%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wouldn't%20say%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20place%20immediately%20that%20I%20could%20live.%20Being%20from%20New%20Jersey%20and%20living%20outside%20New%20York%20City%20my%20whole%20life%2C%20it's%20very%20diverse%20and%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20things%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20obviously%20not%20as%20big%20as%20New%20York%2C%20there%20are%20also%20things%20to%20do%20in%20Charleston.%20You%20can%20hike%2C%20there%20are%20cultural%20events%20in%20the%20city%20and%20also%20outside%20the%20city%2C%20there's%20an%20area%20called%20Summerville%20that%20also%20has%20those%20things.%20I%20could%20very%20much%20picture%20myself%20in%20there%20because%20of%20the%20variety%20of%20things%20the%20area%20has%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20the%20weather%20%E2%80%94%20no%20snow%2C%20none%20of%20that%20to%20deal%20with.%20The%20weather%20and%20being%20outdoors%20all%20year%20round.%20When%20I%20was%20younger%20I%20used%20to%20be%20a%20winter%20person%20where%20I%20liked%20to%20ski%20and%20all%20that.%20But%20now%20I%20like%20being%20able%20to%20enjoy%20life%20and%20be%20outside%20and%20in%20a%20mild%20climate%20with%20lots%20of%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOur%20house%20in%20South%20Carolina%20isn't%20cheaper%2C%20but%20we%20got%20more%20bang%20for%20our%20buck%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20I%20was%20in%20that%20house%20for%2027%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpendoor%20purchased%20the%20home%20from%20me%20free%20and%20clear%20for%20somewhere%20around%20%24493%2C000.%20The%20company%20then%20put%20the%20home%20on%20the%20market%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20ago%20and%20it%20was%20sold%20within%20a%20week%20to%20another%20buyer.%20%3Cem%3E(Editor's%20note%3A%20The%20Zillow%20listing%20says%20the%20home%20sale%20is%20pending%20for%20%24540%2C000.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20bought%20the%20house%20for%20%24143%2C000%20in%201997.%20It%20was%20about%201%2C300%20square%20feet%2C%20ranch%20style%2C%20with%20three%20bedrooms%20and%20two%20baths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20house%20in%20South%20Carolina%20is%20in%20a%20suburb%20called%20Moncks%20Corner%2C%20about%2030%20miles%20from%20Charleston%20proper.%20The%20feel%20of%20the%20town%20is%20a%20lot%20like%20Butler%2C%20except%20with%20beautiful%20weather%20and%20palm%20trees.%20There's%20a%20huge%2C%20huge%20lake%20two%20miles%20from%20where%20the%20house%20is%20being%20built.%20I%20can%20get%20to%20the%20beach%20easily%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20the%20beaches%20are%20free%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20can%20get%20to%20the%20city%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%20it's%20not%20New%20York%20City%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20a%20city%20and%20just%20a%20more%20laid-back%20life.%20You%20have%20great%20food%2C%20and%20some%20entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20less%20there%20and%20there%20are%20far%20lower%20taxes%20on%20property%20and%20payroll.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20as%20much%20in%20savings%20as%20you%20would%20think.%20That%20area%20is%20really%20booming.%20It's%20growing%20and%20there's%20building%20like%20crazy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20house%20that%20we%20bought%20in%20Charleston%20was%20%24433%2C000%2C%20but%20the%20square%20footage%20is%20more%20than%20we%20had%20in%20New%20Jersey.%20It's%20a%20brand-new%20build%20in%20a%20brand-new%20development%2C%20which%20goes%20towards%20the%20quality%20of%20life.%20We%20could%20not%20have%20afforded%20that%20build%20in%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltogether%2C%20there%20are%20three%20bedrooms%20and%20two%20full%20baths%20on%20the%20first%20floor%2C%20and%20then%20a%20lofted%20area%20makes%20it%20four%20bedrooms.%20So%20if%20we%20have%20guests%2C%20or%20my%20daughter%20comes%20home%20to%20live%20with%20us%2C%20it's%20almost%20like%20an%20additional%20self-contained%20space%20away%20from%20the%20main%20parts%20of%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20really%20nice%20to%20have%20that%20area%20of%20the%20house%20that%20we%20didn't%20have%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20the%20yard%20is%20actually%20a%20little%20bit%20bigger%20than%20we%20had%20in%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWould%20we%20have%20moved%20here%20if%20our%20daughter%20was%20here%3F%20Probably%20not%2C%20because%20I%20hadn't%20been%20to%20the%20area.%20She's%20a%20senior%20now%20and%20an%20athlete%2C%20so%20I%20go%20down%20to%20Charleston%20at%20least%20four%20or%20five%20times%20a%20year%20to%20see%20her%20events%20and%20stay%20with%20her%20or%20in%20a%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I'm%20not%20so%20sure%20if%2C%20had%20I%20not%20had%20those%20experiences%20and%20been%20down%20there%2C%20that%20Charleston%20would%20necessarily%20have%20been%20on%20my%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-south-carolina-retirement-taxes-weather-cost-of-living-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712869485000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66184b6a1caec1275a6f58b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-south-carolina-retirement-taxes-weather-cost-of-living-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kathie%20Zucker%20and%20her%20husband%20are%20moving%20to%20South%20Carolina%20to%20bask%20in%2