og's%20head%20above%20the%20water%2C%20a%20feature%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbondvet.com%2Fabout-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Gabrielle%20Fadl%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20medical%20director%20and%20veterinarian%20at%20Bond%20Vet%2C%20likes%20to%20see%20in%20a%20dog%20life%20vest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20extra-small%20and%20small%20sizes%20have%20one%20solid%2C%20padded%20handle%20for%20pulling%20a%20pup%20out%20of%20the%20water%2C%20the%20larger%20jackets%20have%20two%20handles%20for%20better%20leverage.%20The%20vest%20comes%20with%20multiple%20reflective%20accents%20that%20improve%20the%20likelihood%20of%20spotting%20a%20dog%20in%20the%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20small%20dogs%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20small%20dogs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20dog%20life%20jackets%20for%20smaller%20breeds%20should%20have%20the%20right%20balance%20of%20buoyancy%20and%20comfort%20without%20so%20much%20foam%20or%20fabric%20that%20it%20overwhelms%20little%20swimmers.%20The%20Ruffwear%20Float%20Coat%20Dog%20Life%20Jacket%20has%20a%20tailored%20fit%20packed%20with%20foam%20flotation%20that%20doesn't%20hinder%20the%20movement%20of%20short%20legs.%20While%20the%20jacket%20will%20work%20for%20any%20size%20dog%2C%20its%20snug%20fit%20and%20small%20sizes%20will%20keep%20pups%20afloat%20in%20the%20water%20without%20compromising%20mobility%20or%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20and%20Kristi%20Jagger%2C%20dog%20surfing%20instructors%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.socalsurfdogs.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESo%20Cal%20Surf%20Dogs%20Club%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20say%20that%20this%20jacket%20fits%20the%20best%2C%20and%20the%20handle%20on%20top%20of%20the%20coat%20makes%20for%20easy%20water%20retrieval.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F25813850%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2014%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20identified%20this%20vest%20as%20the%20best%20of%20those%20tested%20for%20keeping%20an%20incapacitated%20dog%20afloat%20in%20open%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Float%20Coat%20wraps%20around%20the%20belly%20and%20secures%20with%20two%20adjustable%20buckle%20straps.%20The%20chest%20strap%20has%20an%20adjustable%20telescoping%20design%20that%20slips%20over%20the%20head%20to%20fit%20different%20neck%20sizes.%20Depending%20on%20fit%2C%20the%20belly%20straps%20may%20partially%20rub%20against%20the%20skin%20or%20cause%20discomfort.%20Its%20nylon%20sides%20packed%20with%20closed-cell%20foam%20helps%20keep%20a%20dog%20upright%20while%20swimming.%20There's%20a%20sturdy%20handle%20sewn%20into%20the%20back%20of%20the%20vest%20and%20a%20D-ring%20where%20you%20can%20attach%20a%20leash%20and%20a%20loop%20for%20hanging%20a%20light.%20It%20does%20not%20have%20a%20chin%20float.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20jacket%20comes%20in%20three%20bright%20colors%2C%20but%20McGlynn%20recommends%20skipping%20the%20blue%20one%2C%20which%20would%20be%20harder%20to%20see%20in%20the%20water%2C%20even%20with%20the%20vest's%20reflective%20trim.%20Like%20all%20Ruffwear%20products%2C%20the%20Float%20Coat%20comes%20with%20a%20hefty%20price%20tag%2C%20but%20with%20its%20durable%20construction%2C%20the%20high-quality%20jacket%20will%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20large%20dogs%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20large%20dogs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Surf%20N'%20Turf%20Dog%20Life%20Jacket%20is%20built%20tough%20for%20large%2C%20active%20dogs.%20The%20vest%20earned%20the%20highest%20score%20for%20extra-large%20pups%20in%20the%20BoatUS%20Foundation's%20evaluation.%20Testers%20particularly%20liked%20its%20two%20lifting%20handles%20for%20hauling%20a%20dog%20out%20of%20the%20water%20and%20its%20scalloped%20design%2C%20which%20fits%20the%20shoulders%20and%20rear%20haunches%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20vest%20is%20the%20most%20versatile%20option%20among%20the%20best%20dog%20life%20jackets%20we%20evaluated.%20It%20has%20two%20detachable%20layers%2C%20one%20stuffed%20with%20foam%20for%20flotation%2C%20the%20other%20a%20simple%20nylon%20ripstop%20shell%20that%20your%20dog%20can%20wear%20as%20an%20extra%20layer%20for%20on-land%20adventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20heavy-duty%20vest%20has%20two%20adjustable%20buckle%20straps%20on%20its%20belly%20panel%20and%20a%20third%20adjustable%20strap%20at%20the%20chest.%20Two%20metal%20D-rings%20are%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20vest%2C%20and%20one%20doubles%20as%20a%20bottle%20opener.%20However%2C%20the%20jacket%20lacks%20a%20chin%20float.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Surf%20N'%20Turf%20comes%20in%20five%20sizes%20and%20two%20colors%20with%20reflective%20trim.%20While%20the%20jacket%20is%20moderately%20pricey%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20Kurgo's%20lifetime%20guarantee%20against%20manufacturing%20defects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20neoprene%20jacket%5C%22%3EBest%20neoprene%20jacket%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENeoprene%20dog%20life%20jackets%20are%20less%20bulky%20and%20often%20more%20comfortable%20than%20other%20vests.%20They%20also%20have%20insulation%20to%20keep%20a%20dog's%20body%20temperature%20from%20dropping%20drastically%20in%20cold%20water.%20Even%20with%20its%20sleek%20design%2C%20the%20side%20panels%20of%20the%20Dawson%20Swim%20Life%20Jacket%20are%20packed%20with%20plenty%20of%20foam%20to%20keep%20novice%20swimmers%20afloat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jacket%20has%20a%20neoprene%20belly%20panel%20fitted%20with%20two%20adjustable%20buckles.%20A%20third%20adjustable%20strap%20at%20the%20chest%20has%20a%20float%20to%20help%20keep%20a%20dog's%20head%20above%20water.%20Unlike%20some%20of%20the%20other%20designs%20in%20this%20guide%2C%20the%20straps%20make%20contact%20with%20the%20dog's%20skin%20at%20the%20edges%3B%20this%20could%20cause%20some%20discomfort%20and%20rubbing%20after%20a%20long%20day%20in%20the%20water%2C%20especially%20if%20your%20pup%20has%20a%20barrel%20chest%20or%20a%20chubby%20belly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20life%20vest%20comes%20in%20five%20sizes.%20The%20extra-small%20and%20small%20sizes%20have%20one%20sturdy%20handle%20at%20the%20back%20for%20lifting%20a%20dog%20out%20of%20the%20water%20in%20an%20emergency%2C%20while%20the%20larger%20sizes%20have%20two%20straps%20for%20better%20leverage.%20Reflective%20accents%20provide%20better%20visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20dog%20life%20jacket%20evaluation%2C%20the%20BoatUS%20Foundation%20found%20that%20thinner%20neoprene%20vests%20tend%20to%20bunch%20up%20less%20on%20a%20dog%20who%20is%20sitting%20or%20lying%20down%20out%20of%20the%20water%2C%20making%20them%20more%20comfortable%20overall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20dog%20life%20jacket%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20input%20from%20our%20experts%2C%20we%20came%20up%20with%20the%20following%20list%20of%20features%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20life%20jacket%20for%20dogs%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20sturdy%20handle%20for%20small%20dogs%2C%20two%20for%20large%20dogs%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20support%20panel%20or%20thick%20straps%20under%20the%20belly%20to%20help%20lift%20a%20dog%20out%20of%20the%20water%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFoam%20placement%20that%20won't%20cause%20discomfort%20when%20a%20dog%20is%20sitting%20or%20lying%20down%20on%20land%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESturdy%2C%20adjustable%20buckles%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBright%20colors%20that%20can%20be%20easily%20seen%20in%20the%20water%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EReflective%20accents%20for%20added%20visibility%20in%20the%20water%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20chin%20float%20to%20help%20keep%20the%20head%20above%20water%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAvailable%20in%20brick-and-mortar%20stores%20to%20try%20on%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20selected%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20selected%20the%20best%20dog%20life%20jackets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20standards%20or%20certifications%20to%20guide%20pet%20caretakers%20in%20selecting%20a%20quality%20dog%20life%20jacket.%20%26quot%3BUnlike%20human%20flotation%20devices%2C%20canine%20flotation%20devices%20are%20not%20regulated%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.centerforpetsafety.org%2Fwho-is-cps%2Fthe-cps-team%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELindsey%20Wolko%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.centerforpetsafety.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECenter%20for%20Pet%20Safety%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20very%20little%20scientific%20examination%20of%20the%20flotation%20needs%20of%20pets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20guide%20to%20the%20best%20dog%20life%20jackets%2C%20we%20relied%20on%20the%20recommendations%20of%20experts%20and%20two%20studies%20conducted%20on%20dog%20life%20vests.%20Then%20we%20reviewed%20life%20vests%20on%20the%20market%20and%20selected%20the%20ones%20that%20met%20most%2C%20if%20not%20all%2C%20of%20our%20experts'%20criteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20quoted%20in%20this%20article%20include%20a%20veterinarian%2C%20a%20pet%20safety%20expert%2C%20and%20an%20editor%20for%20BoatUS%20Magazine%2C%20the%20official%20publication%20of%20the%20BoatUS.%20We%20also%20spoke%20with%20Gigi%20Bagaporo%2C%20Mark%20Jagger%2C%20and%20Kristi%20Jagger%2C%20surfing%20instructors%20with%20the%20So%20Cal%20Surf%20Dogs%20Club.%20The%20organization%20helps%20pups%20prep%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fanimalcenter.org%2Fsurf-dog-surf-a-thon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHelen%20Woodward%20Animal%20Center's%20Annual%20Surf%20Dog%20Surf-a-Thon%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3ELife%20jackets%20for%20dogs%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhen%20should%20a%20dog%20wear%20a%20life%20jacket%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAnytime%20a%20dog%20is%20in%20or%20around%20water%2C%20a%20life%20vest%20is%20worth%20considering.%20Accidents%20can%20happen%20even%20if%20you%20have%20a%20strong%20swimmer.%20A%20dog%20should%20wear%20a%20life%20vest%20while%20floating%2C%20kayaking%2C%20stand-up%20paddleboarding%2C%20or%20surfing.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20dog%20owners%20use%20them%20for%20fun%20on%20the%20beach%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20McGlynn.%20%26quot%3BJust%20swimming%20and%20retrieving%2C%20there%20could%20be%20currents%20that%20pull%20them%20out.%26quot%3B%20Wolko%20says%20it's%20up%20to%20pet%20guardians%20to%20determine%20whether%20their%20dog%20should%20wear%20a%20life%20jacket%20based%20on%20their%20experience%20in%20and%20around%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EShould%20my%20dog%20wear%20a%20life%20jacket%20around%20the%20pool%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20dog%20that%20has%20spent%20little%20time%20around%20a%20pool%2C%20Wolko%20says%20putting%20them%20in%20a%20life%20vest%20is%20a%20good%20idea.%20Only%20after%20a%20dog%20has%20been%20properly%20introduced%20to%20a%20pool%2C%20including%20how%20to%20use%20the%20stairs%20to%20exit%20the%20water%2C%20is%20it%20OK%20for%20strong-swimming%20dogs%20to%20go%20without%20a%20life%20vest.%20Even%20if%20your%20dog%20has%20pool%20experience%2C%20they%20should%20wear%20a%20life%20vest%20when%20visiting%20unfamiliar%20pools%20that%20may%20be%20designed%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20color%20life%20jacket%20is%20easiest%20to%20spot%20in%20the%20water%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20experts%20we%20consulted%20told%20us%20the%20best%20dog%20life%20jackets%20are%20easiest%20to%20spot%20in%20the%20water%20when%20they%20are%20brightly%20colored.%20%26quot%3BColors%20like%20blue%20and%20gray%20are%20not%20going%20to%20stand%20out%20as%20well%20in%20the%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20McGlynn.%20Reflective%20accents%20on%20the%20exterior%20also%20improve%20visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20a%20dog%20drown%20while%20wearing%20a%20life%20jacket%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20A%20dog%20can%20drown%20while%20wearing%20a%20life%20vest.%20%26quot%3BDogs%20who%20are%20not%20well%20supported%20from%20a%20flotation%20perspective%20can%20panic%20or%20tire%20from%20treading%20water%2C%20increasing%20the%20risk%20of%20drowning%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Wolko.%20McGlynn%20says%20that%20dogs%20wearing%20life%20jackets%20may%20also%20face%20extreme%20danger%20if%20they%20become%20trapped%20under%20the%20water%20or%20if%20waves%20or%20rapids%20splash%20in%20their%20nose%20and%20mouth.%20A%20life%20jacket%20that%20is%20properly%20fitted%20can%20help%20minimize%20the%20risk%2C%20as%20can%20educating%20yourself%20about%20canine%20water%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20you%20measure%20your%20dog%20for%20a%20life%20jacket%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20life%20jacket%20that%20fits%20properly%20is%20essential%20to%20keeping%20a%20dog%20safe%20in%20and%20around%20the%20water.%20The%20best%20way%20to%20ensure%20proper%20fit%20is%20to%20take%20your%20pup%20into%20a%20brick-and-mortar%20store%20to%20try%20your%20options%20rather%20than%20ordering%20online%2C%20according%20to%20several%20of%20our%20experts.%20Because%20dogs%20come%20in%20so%20many%20different%20shapes%20and%20sizes%2C%20what%20fits%20one%20comfortably%20may%20not%20be%20appropriate%20for%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20fitting%20a%20dog%20for%20a%20life%20jacket%2C%20McGlynn%20told%20us%20to%20look%20for%20a%20vest%20that%20fits%20snugly%20but%20has%20no%20buckles%20or%20straps%20tight%20enough%20to%20ride%20up%20or%20rub%20against%20the%20skin.%20She%20also%20suggested%20examining%20how%20the%20life%20jacket%20fits%20when%20a%20dog%20is%20lying%20down%20and%20standing%20up.%20If%20your%20dog%20wears%20a%20life%20vest%20for%20several%20hours%2C%20it%20should%20be%20comfortable%20in%20every%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChest%20girth%2C%20neck%20girth%2C%20and%20weight%20are%20also%20crucial%20considerations%20when%20fitting%20a%20dog%20with%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20life%20jackets.%20Take%20the%20following%20measurements%20to%20narrow%20down%20the%20right%20size%20for%20your%20pup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChest%20girth%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20dog%20life%20vest%20is%20fitted%20according%20to%20the%20width%20and%20shape%20of%20a%20dog's%20chest.%20To%20get%20their%20chest%20girth%2C%20measure%20the%20circumference%20around%20the%20widest%20part%20of%20the%20chest%20right%20behind%20the%20front%20legs.%20You'll%20get%20the%20most%20accurate%20reading%20when%20your%20dog%20is%20standing%20in%20a%20relaxed%20position.%20If%20their%20chest%20girth%20falls%20between%20sizes%2C%20choose%20the%20larger%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENeck%20girth%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20dog%20life%20vest%20should%20not%20be%20so%20tight%20around%20the%20front%20of%20the%20chest%20and%20neck%20that%20it%20may%20press%20against%20the%20windpipe.%20To%20determine%20girth%2C%20measure%20the%20circumference%20of%20your%20dog's%20neck%20around%20its%20thickest%20part%2C%20just%20below%20the%20collar.%20When%20in%20doubt%2C%20size%20up!%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhile%20you%20can't%20fit%20a%20dog%20for%20a%20life%20jacket%20by%20knowing%20their%20weight%20alone%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20ensure%20the%20vest%20size%20can%20support%20their%20weight%20in%20the%20water.%20If%20your%20dog%20is%20heavier%20than%20recommended%20for%20the%20life%20jacket%20that%20fits%20them%20best%2C%20either%20size%20up%20or%20look%20for%20a%20different%20brand%20labeled%20for%20their%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20all%20dogs%20swim%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20doggy%20paddling%20is%20instinctual%20to%20many%20dogs%2C%20not%20all%20dogs%20know%20how%20to%20swim%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Fadl.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20crucial%20to%20allow%20your%20dog%20time%20to%20learn%2C%20and%20their%20time%20in%20the%20water%20should%20always%20be%20supervised%20for%20their%20safety.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20dogs%20are%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20danger%20in%20the%20water%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20dogs%20are%20natural%20water%20babies%2C%20while%20others%20may%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20experience%20challenges%20even%20if%20they've%20entered%20the%20water%20willingly.%20McGlynn%20told%20us%20that%20older%20pups%20or%20those%20with%20limited%20mobility%20may%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20tire%20while%20swimming%2C%20leaving%20them%20more%20susceptible%20to%20dangers%20like%20rip%20currents.%20Dogs%20with%20lower%20body%20fat%2C%20like%20greyhounds%20and%20boxers%2C%20may%20also%20struggle%20in%20the%20water%20if%20their%20body%20temperature%20drops%20too%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3A%20Outward%20Hound%20Granby%20Splash%20Life%20Jacket%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20corgi%20wearing%20an%20orange%20life%20jacket%20is%20standing%20on%20a%20sandy%20beach.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b190289751e300192a292d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20vest%20from%20Outward%20Hound%20topped%20our%20list%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20life%20jackets%20thanks%20to%20its%20excellent%20performance.%3Cp%3EChewy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENeoprene%20belly%20band%2C%20three%20adjustable%20straps%2C%20foam%20chin%20float%2C%20larger%20sizes%20have%20two%20lifting%20handles%2C%20reflective%20accents%20for%20better%20visibility%2C%20available%20in%20five%20sizes%20and%20four%20colors%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHand-wash%20only%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAvailable%20sizes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%205%20sizes%20for%20chests%20from%2011%20to%2044%20inches%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EColor%20options%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Orange%2C%20pink%2C%20yellow%2C%20green%20camo%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECare%20instructions%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Hand-wash%2C%20air-dry%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20your%20dog%20is%20big%20or%20small%2C%20a%20natural%20swimmer%20or%20a%20natural%20sinker%2C%20the%20Granby%20Splash%20Life%20Jacket%20offers%20protection%20and%20comfort%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20water.%20In%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boatus.org%2Ffindings%2F51%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2012%20dog%20life%20jacket%20evaluation%3C%2Fa%3E%20conducted%20by%20the%20BoatUS%20Foundation%2C%20the%20testing%20team%20found%20the%20Granby%20excelled%20in%20every%20category%20for%20dogs%20of%20all%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20BoatUS%20Foundation%20found%20the%20jacket's%20evenly%20distributed%20flotation%20foam%20kept%20a%20dog%20horizontal%20in%20the%20water.%20Dogs%20wearing%20the%20vest%20appeared%20comfortable%20out%20of%20the%20water%2C%20and%20their%20movement%20was%20unrestricted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Granby%20Splash%20Life%20Jacket%20has%20buoyant%20foam%20panels%20concealed%20within%20a%20rip-resistant%20nylon%20shell.%20A%20flexible%20neoprene%20band%20with%20three%20Velcro%20straps%20and%20two%20adjustable%2C%20quick-release%20buckle%20straps%20wraps%20around%20the%20belly.%20A%20third%20strap%20buckles%20at%20the%20chest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20foam%20chin%20panel%20on%20the%20chest%20strap%20helps%20keep%20a%20dog's%20head%20above%20the%20water%2C%20a%20feature%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbondvet.com%2Fabout-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Gabrielle%20Fadl%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20medical%20director%20and%20veterinarian%20at%20Bond%20Vet%2C%20likes%20to%20see%20in%20a%20dog%20life%20vest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20extra-small%20and%20small%20sizes%20have%20one%20solid%2C%20padded%20handle%20for%20pulling%20a%20pup%20out%20of%20the%20water%2C%20the%20larger%20jackets%20have%20two%20handles%20for%20better%20leverage.%20The%20vest%20comes%20with%20multiple%20reflective%20accents%20that%20improve%20the%20likelihood%20of%20spotting%20a%20dog%20in%20the%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20neoprene%20jacket%3A%20Outward%20Hound%20Dawson%20Sw