3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvesting%20in%20basket%20portfolios%20is%20similar%20to%20buying%20a%20meal%20kit%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lannan.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20automatically%20provided%20with%20the%20right%20recipe%20and%20ingredients.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFidelity%20Youth%20Baskets%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20lack%20this%20flexibility.%20Teens%20investing%20in%20a%20Youth%20Basket%20portfolio%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20add%20or%20remove%20investments%20outside%20the%20three%20pre-built%20teen-inspired%20thematic%20baskets%2C%20nor%20can%20they%20adjust%20the%20target%20weights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Youth%20thematic%20baskets%20aim%20to%20ease%20teens%20into%20stock%20trading%20with%20simplified%20investing%20strategies%20while%20mitigating%20portfolio%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Frisk-vs-volatility%5C%22%3Erisk%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20lack%20of%20flexibility%2C%20while%20limiting%2C%20can%20prevent%20teens%20from%20investing%20in%20volatile%20or%20high-risk%20assets%20like%20mutual%20funds%2C%20REITs%2C%20or%20crypto.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBaskets%20add%20an%20element%20of%20diversification%2C%26quot%3B%20Said%20Lannan.%20%26quot%3BRather%20than%20investing%20in%20a%20single%20security%2C%20teens%20invest%20in%20a%20whole%20portfolio%20of%20different%20securities.%20This%20helps%20balance%20out%20some%20of%20the%20risks%20that%20come%20along%20with%20investing.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERisk%20is%20also%20mitigated%20through%20the%20app's%20curated%20video%20content.%20Before%20investing%20in%20one%20of%20the%20Youth%20Baskets%2C%20users%20are%20greeted%20with%20an%20educational%20video%20featuring%20one%20of%20the%20basket's%20creators.%20%26quot%3BPairing%20investments%20with%20education%20offers%20a%20way%20for%20teens%20to%20build%20up%20confidence%20even%20before%20clicking%20on%20the%20portfolios%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lannan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20Invest%20in%20Fidelity%20Youth%20Baskets%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20invest%20in%20Fidelity%20Youth%20Baskets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20aged%2013-17%20with%20an%20active%20Fidelity%20Youth%20account%20can%20invest%20in%20Fidelity%20Youth%20Baskets%20free%20of%20subscriptions%20or%20additional%20fees.%20Parents%20with%20an%20existing%20Fidelity%20account%20can%20open%20Youth%20accounts%20on%20behalf%20of%20a%20child.%20Once%20signed%20up%2C%20teens%20can%20download%20the%20free%20Fidelity%20Youth%20app%20on%20their%20mobile%20devices%20and%20activate%20their%20accounts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20a%20custodial%20account%2C%20teens%20are%20fully%20in%20charge%20of%20managing%20their%20Youth%20investment%20portfolios.%20Parents%20can%20still%20track%20and%20monitor%20their%20teen's%20account%2C%20but%20they'll%20be%20unable%20to%20make%20withdrawals%20or%20transactions%20on%20behalf%20of%20their%20kids.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Are%20Fidelity%20Youth%20Baskets%20Right%20For%20You%3F%C2%A0%5C%22%3EAre%20Fidelity%20Youth%20Baskets%20right%20for%20you%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFidelity's%20new%20Youth%20Basket%20portfolios%20provide%20an%20accessible%2C%20straightforward%20way%20for%20young%20investors%20to%20manage%20a%20diversified%20portfolio%20of%20investable%20securities.%20If%20you're%20between%2013%20and%2017%20years%20old%2C%20basket%20investing%20through%20Fidelity%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20build%20upon%20existing%20investing%20knowledge%20and%20get%20hands-on%20experience%20managing%20a%20diversified%20portfolio%20of%20stocks%20and%20ETFs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20earlier%20you%20start%2C%20the%20better%20off%20you%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lannan.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20the%20importance%20of%20starting%20early.%20With%20Fidelity%2C%20we're%20trying%20to%20help%20teens%20and%20their%20parents%20build%20money-managing%20skills.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Fidelity%20Youth%20Baskets%20are%20inexpensive.%20There%20are%20no%20additional%20minimums%2C%20subscription%20fees%2C%20or%20commissions.%20You%20can%20start%20investing%20for%20as%20little%20as%20%241.%20Investors%2018%20and%20up%20must%20pay%20the%20%244.99%20subscription%20fee%20to%20access%20Fidelity%20Basket%20Portfolios.%20So%2C%20if%20you're%20teen%20is%20nearing%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20this%20may%20be%20a%20drawback.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20important%20to%20mention%20that%20Fidelity%20Youth%20is%20not%20a%20custodial%20UTMA%2FUGMA%20account.%20Parents%20interested%20in%20investing%20and%20managing%20on%20behalf%20of%20a%20child%20until%20they%20are%2018%20(or%2025%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20state)%20shouldn't%20open%20a%20Fidelity%20Youth%20account%20since%20Youth%20accounts%20are%20teen-owned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFidelity%20does%20offer%20a%20custodial%20account%20option%20for%20those%20interested.%20Or%20you%20check%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-custodial-accounts%5C%22%3Ebest%20custodial%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20options.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffidelity-youth-baskets-investment-options-teens-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712865843000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6618242f3f923f7dab06f8a5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffidelity-youth-baskets-investment-options-teens-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fidelity%20demystifies%20investing%20for%20teens%20overwhelmed%20by%20options%20with%20new%20Fidelity%20Youth%20Baskets.%20Here's%20how%20they%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tessa%20Campbell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffidelity-youth-baskets-investment-options-teens-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%2