20watched%20by%20millions%20on%20television.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20acquittal%20in%20October%201995%20after%20nine%20months%20in%20court%20was%20greeted%20with%20disbelief%20by%20many%20Americans%20who%20had%20followed%20every%20twist%20and%20turn%20in%20the%20arguments%20over%20details%20as%20intricate%20as%20whether%20a%20pair%20of%20gloves%20really%20fitted%20the%20former%20athlete's%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20April%2010th%2C%20our%20father%2C%20Orenthal%20James%20Simpson%2C%20succumbed%20to%20his%20battle%20with%20cancer%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20message%20signed%20by%20the%20family%20said%20Thursday%20on%20social%20media%20site%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20surrounded%20by%20his%20children%20and%20grandchildren.%20During%20this%20time%20of%20transition%2C%20his%20family%20asks%20that%20you%20please%20respect%20their%20wishes%20for%20privacy%20and%20grace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20reportedly%20been%20battling%20prostate%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EElite%20athlete%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimpson%20grew%20up%20in%20poverty%20and%20ill%20health%20but%20developed%20into%20an%20elite%20athlete%2C%20rising%20rapidly%20to%20stardom%20first%20as%20a%20college%20football%20player%20and%20then%20in%20the%20National%20Football%20League%2C%20where%20he%20won%20the%201973%20Most%20Valuable%20Player%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Heisman%20Trophy%20Trust%2C%20which%20presents%20an%20annual%20award%20for%20top%20college%20football%20players%2C%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bmourns%20the%20passing%20of%201968%20Heisman%20Trophy%20Winner%20O.J.%20Simpson.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20popularity%20only%20grew%20with%20a%20post-NFL%20career%20as%20an%20actor%20and%20an%20ad%20pitchman%2C%20where%20his%20appearances%20promoting%20everything%20from%20orange%20juice%20to%20car%20rentals%20made%20him%20one%20of%20the%20most%20recognizable%20Black%20faces%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20work%20with%20Hertz%20in%20particular%2C%20where%20he%20was%20shown%20sprinting%20through%20airports%20while%20wearing%20a%20three-piece%20suit%2C%20became%20part%20of%20pop%20culture%20folklore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20all%20came%20to%20an%20abrupt%20end%20on%20June%2012%2C%201994%20when%20Brown%20Simpson%2C%2035%2C%20and%20waiter%20Goldman%2C%2025%2C%20were%20found%20stabbed%20to%20death%20outside%20her%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20views%20on%20whether%20Simpson%20was%20guilty%20or%20innocent%20of%20murder%20divided%20sharply%20along%20racial%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20although%20allowed%20to%20walk%20free%2C%20there%20was%20no%20happy%20next%20chapter%20for%20%26quot%3BO.J.%26quot%3B%20--%20or%20%26quot%3BThe%20Juice%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20was%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimpson%20was%20subsequently%20found%20liable%20for%20the%20deaths%20in%20a%201997%20civil%20suit%20and%20was%20ordered%20to%20pay%20damages%20totaling%20%2433.5%20million%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFred%20Goldman%2C%20Ronald's%20father%2C%20spoke%20to%20NBC%20News%20Thursday%20and%20described%20Simpson's%20death%20as%20%26quot%3Bno%20great%20loss.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20thing%20I%20have%20to%20say%20is%20it's%20just%20further%20reminder%20of%20Ron%20being%20gone%20all%20these%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimpson%20also%20served%20nearly%20nine%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20a%20bungled%20armed%20robbery%2C%20before%20a%20parole%20board%20in%20the%20western%20state%20of%20Nevada%20approved%20his%20release%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDismissed%20health%20concerns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20public's%20fascination%20never%20waned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BO.J.%3A%20Made%20in%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20nearly%20eight-hour%20documentary%20about%20his%20murder%20trial%2C%20won%20the%20best%20documentary%20Oscar%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20%26q