reservations%20and%20dropped%20plans%20to%20visit%20Maldives.%20The%20tourism%20arrival%20statistics%20reflected%20how%20from%20being%20a%20top%20visitor%20country%2C%20India's%20position%20went%20down%20to%20first%20fifth%20and%20now%20at%20the%20sixth%20position%20after%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20statistics%20by%20the%20Maldives'%20Ministry%20of%20Tourism%2C%20this%20year%20as%20of%20April%2010%2C%20of%20the%20total%206%2C63%2C269%20tourists%20arriving%2C%20China%20continued%20to%20lead%20with%2071%2C995%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20(66%2C999)%2C%20Russia%20(66%2C803)%2C%20Italy%20(61%2C379)%2C%20Germany%20(52%2C256)%20and%20India%20(37%2C417).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20discussions%20took%20place%20at%20a%20meeting%20held%20at%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20in%20Male%2C%20MATATO%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20they%20expressed%20their%20intention%20to%20collaborate%20closely%20with%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20in%20Maldives%20to%20bolster%20tourism%20initiatives%2C%20Sun.mv%20news%20portal%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20trajectory%2C%20plans%20are%20currently%20underway%20to%20launch%20comprehensive%20road%20shows%20across%20key%20Indian%20cities%20and%20to%20facilitate%20influencer%20and%20media%20familiarisation%20trips%20to%20the%20Maldives%20in%20the%20upcoming%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20quoting%20from%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20India%20remains%20a%20crucial%20tourist%20market%20to%20the%20Maldives%2C%20MATATO%20states%20they%20look%20forward%20to%20partnering%20with%20prominent%20travel%20associations%20and%20industry%20stakeholders%20across%20India%20to%20further%20promote%20the%20Maldives%20as%20a%20premier%20travel%20destination%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Association%20also%20attributed%20its%20meeting%20with%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20testament%20to%20MATATO's%20continued%20dedication%20to%20fostering%20robust%20tourism%20ties%20between%20the%20Maldives%20and%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20it%20said%2C%20will%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20%26quot%3Btransformative%20collaborations%20to%20drive%20sustainable%20growth%20in%20the%20region's%20tourism%20sector.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20before%20this%20diplomatic%20row%20erupted%2C%20Maldives%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20had%2C%20within%20hours%20of%20taking%20oath%20last%20November%2C%20asked%20India%20to%20withdraw%20its%2088%20military%20personnel%20from%20the%20country%2C%20saying%20their%20presence%20was%20a%20threat%20to%20his%20country's%20sovereignty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu%2C%20known%20for%20his%20pro-China%20leanings%2C%20has%20announced%20that%20no%20Indian%20military%20personnel%2C%20even%20in%20civilian%20clothes%2C%20would%20be%20present%20in%20Maldives%20after%20all%20of%2088%20personnel%20are%20repatriated%20by%20May%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712858100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fp8384mso_maldives-generic_625x300_08_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmaldives-to-hold-roadshows-in-india-to-boost-travel-amid-strained-ties-5421329%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20apparent%20bid%20to%20woo%20Indian%20tourists%20back%20to%20the%20Maldives%2C%20a%20major%20tourism%20body%20in%20Male%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20hold%20road%20shows%20across%20key%20Indian%20cities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmaldives-to-hold-roadshows-in-india-to-boost-travel-amid-strained-ties-5421329%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmald