%20credibility%2C%20thanks%20to%20leaders%20with%20%26quot%3BLeftist%20views%26quot%3B%20who%20are%20arrogant%20enough%20to%20ignore%20feedback%20from%20the%20grassroot%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20did%20not%20name%20anyone%2C%20he%20made%20his%20target%20clear%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20person%20who%20is%20handling%20communications%20for%20the%20party%26quot%3B.%20This%20leader%2C%20Mr%20Gupta%20said%2C%20not%20only%20failed%20to%20call%20up%20when%20his%20father%20was%20ailing%20and%20in%20hospital%2C%20he%20was%20also%20responsible%20for%20much%20of%20the%20garbled%20messages%20emanating%20from%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEver%20since%20he%20has%20taken%20charge%2C%20there%20has%20been%20many%20issues%2C%20nationalism%2C%20Sanatan%2C%20alliances%20with%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party...%20I%20along%20with%20many%20others%20were%20extremely%20upset.%20But%20we%20soldiered%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20final%20straw%20was%20when%20he%20did%20not%20receive%20even%20a%20courtesy%20call%20about%20his%20father.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20it%20was%20time%20to%20call%20it%20a%20day...%20It%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20self-respect%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gupta%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Congress%20is%20yet%20to%20comment%20on%20his%20departure%20--%20Mr%20Gupta%20is%20the%20latest%20of%20a%20string%20of%20leaders%20from%20the%20party's%20communications%20section%20to%20leave%20--%20he%20tackled%20the%20thorny%20issue%20of%20the%20party's%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20anyone%20leaves%20they%20are%20criticised%20--%20'He%20left%20because%20of%20greed.%20He%20was%20scared'%20--%20what%20about%20self-respect%3F%20When%20people%20like%20us%20give%20feedback%20from%20the%20ground%2C%20it%20should%20be%20heard.%20Leaders%20who%20cannot%20listen%20should%20not%20be%20given%20a%20free%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20why%20he%20decided%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20he%20has%20been%20criticising%20so%20strongly%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%20it%20was%20about%20the%20long-term%20vision%20of%20the%20party.%20The%20BJP%20today%20stands%20for%20everything%20the%20Congress%20once%20represented%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BPrimarily%20the%20two%20core%20values%20of%20centrist%20policies%20and%20nationalism%2C%20which%20had%20helped%20the%20Congress%20rule%20for%2060%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20these%20values%20have%20been%20overtaken%20by%20Leftist%20ideas%2C%20which%20were%20at%20the%20root%20of%20the%20Congress's%20refusal%20to%20attend%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20temple%20inauguration%20and%20criticism%20of%20businessmen%20who%20contributed%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20was%20never%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20out%20the%20party%20once%20brought%20in%20liberalisation%20and%20stood%20for%20the%20country's%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurning%20away%20from%20the%20temple%20was%20also%20big%20mistake%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20faith%20and%20emotions%20of%20millions%20are%20involved%2C%20one%20should%20not%20ignore%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BYou%20could%20have%20skipped%20the%20inauguration%2C%20but%20could%20have%20easily%20visited%20another%20day%2C'%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20had%20turned%20down%20the%20invite%20for%20the%20temple%20inauguration%2C%20the%20party%20had%20not%20banned%20the%20visit%20for%20any%20leader.%20But%20most%20took%20their%20cue%20from%20them%2C%20and%20barring%20a%20handful%20of%20leaders%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20few%20have%20visited%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20could%20the%20Congress%20lie%20clash%2C%20since%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20in%20the%20habit%20of%20visiting%20temples%2C%20Mr%20Gupta%20said%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20listens%20to%20his%20advisors.%20%26quot%3BBut%20one%20should%20also%20pick%20the%20right%20advisors...%20A%20man%20who%20never%20contested%20elections%2C%20how%20can%20he%20give%20the%20right%20advice%3F%20He%20does%20not%20know%20the%20grassroot%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20he%20intended%20to%20do%20about%20the%20tweets%20that%20berated%20the%20BJP%2C%20whether%20he%20would%20delete%20on%20not%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20ashamed%20of%20my%20past.%20I%20have%20worked%20faithfully%20for%20a%20party%20for%2015%20years.%20But%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20party%20is%20happy%20any%20more%20about%20my%20vision%20or%20mission%20and%20now%20I'm%20trying%20to%20change%20gracefully%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712855340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fv63c3g3o_rohan-gupta_625x300_11_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-another-congress-spokesman-rohan-gupta-joins-bjp-his-parting-shot-5421793%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20spokesperson%20Rohan%20Gupta%20crossed%20over%20to%20the%20BJP%20today%2C%20accusing%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20of%20flipping%20its%20ideology%2C%20giving%20out%20contradictory%20messages%2C%20arrogance%20and%20treading%20on%20people's%20%26quot%3Bself-respect%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-another-congress-spokesman-rohan-gupta-joins-bjp-his-parting-shot-5421793%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-another-congress-spokesman-rohan-gupta-joins-bjp-his-parting-shot-5421793%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-another-congress-spokesman-rohan-gupta-joins-bjp-his-parting-shot-5