0from%20this%20amount%20will%20go%20to%20the%20man's%20daughter%20and%20the%20rest%20to%20his%20widow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712849100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2F40jknnk_best-bus-fare_625x300_09_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fbest-bus-accident-man-killed-while-crossing-road-mumbai-bus-body-told-to-pay-rs-15-6-lakh-to-family-5421309%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Motor%20Accident%20Claims%20Tribunal%20(MACT)%20directed%20Brihanmumbai%20Electric%20Supply%20and%20Transport%20(BEST)%20to%20pay%20Rs%2015.66%20lakh%20as%20compensation%20to%20the%20family%20of%20a%2047-year-old%20man%20who%20died%20in%20an%20accident%20involving%20the%20civic%20undertaking's%20bus.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fbest-bus-accident-man-killed-while-crossing-road-mumbai-bus-body-told-to-pay-rs-15-6-lakh-to-family-5421309%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fbest-bus-accident-man-killed-while-crossing-road-mumbai-bus-body-told-to-pay-rs-15-6-lakh-to-family-5421309%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fbest-bus-accident-man-killed-while-crossing-road-mumbai-bus-body-told-to-pay-rs-15-6-lakh-to-family-5421309%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pregnancy%20May%20Accelerate%20Biological%20Ageing%20In%20Young%20Women%2C%20Says%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWomen%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20sacrifices%20for%20their%20children.%20Now%2C%20a%20new%20study%20has%20revealed%20that%20pregnancy%20can%20speed%20up%20ageing%20in%20young%20mothers.%20Researchers%20at%20the%20Mailman%20School%20of%20Public%20Health%20at%20Columbia%20University%20in%20New%20York%20examined%20the%20reproductive%20histories%20and%20DNA%20samples%20of%201%2C735%20participants%20in%20a%20long-term%2C%20ongoing%20health%20study%20conducted%20in%20the%20Philippines%20to%20examine%20the%20impact%20of%20childbearing%20on%20the%20ageing%20process%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Flifeandstyle%2F2024%2Fapr%2F08%2Fpregnancy-may-speed-up-biological-ageing-study-finds%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20distinct%20%26quot%3Bepigenetic%20clocks%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20genetic%20instruments%20that%20gauge%20biological%20age%20based%20on%20patterns%20of%20a%20process%20known%20as%20DNA%20methylation%2C%20were%20used%20to%20calculate%20the%20ages.%20Every%20pregnancy%20a%20woman%20reported%20was%20associated%20with%20an%20extra%20two%20to%20three%20months%20of%20biological%20ageing%2C%20as%20per%20the%20study%20which%20involved%20825%20young%20women.%20Women%20who%20reported%20more%20pregnancies%20over%20a%20six-year%20follow-up%20period%20also%20demonstrated%20a%20greater%20increase%20in%20biological%20ageing%20during%20that%20time.%20Thus%2C%20they%20found%20women%20who%20had%20been%20pregnant%20in%20the%20past%20looked%20%26quot%3Bbiologically%20older%26quot%3B%20than%20those%20who%20had%20never%20carried%20a%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20the%20investigators%20took%20into%20consideration%20the%20participants'%20environment%2C%20smoking%20habits%2C%20socioeconomic%20level%2C%20and%20genetic%20diversity%2C%20the%20associations%20between%20pregnancy%20and%20biological%20ageing%20remained%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20effect%20was%20not%20reported%20among%20men%2C%20who%20were%20fathers.%20This%20suggests%20that%20the%20effect%20is%20associated%20with%20pregnancy%20or%20breastfeeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20findings%20suggest%20that%20pregnancy%20speeds%20up%20biological%20ageing%2C%20and%20that%20these%20effects%20are%20apparent%20in%20young%2C%20high-fertility%20women.%20Our%20results%20are%20also%20the%20first%20to%20follow%20the%20same%20women%20through%20time%2C%20linking%20changes%20in%20each%20woman's%20pregnancy%20number%20to%20changes%20in%20her%20biological%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Calen%20Ryan%2C%20the%20lead%20author%20and%20an%20associate%20research%20scientist%20in%20the%20Columbia%20Aging%20Center.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20called%20the%20finding%20%26quot%3Bremarkable%26quot%3B%20as%20pregnancy%20is%20linked%20to%20changes%20at%20the%20molecular%20level.%20%26quot%3BIt%20highlights%20how%20we%20have%20been%20overlooking%20pregnancy%20and%20other%20key%20aspects%20of%20women's%20health%20when%20we%20study%20the%20ageing%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ryan%20told%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fhealth%2Fpregnancy-speeds-aging-process-women-study-remarkable-finding%3Fintcmp%3Dtw_fnc%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Fox%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20Ryan%2C%20the%20overall%20effects%20were%20minimal%20and%20might%20be%20associated%20with%20high%20fertility%2C%20inconsistent%20access%20to%20healthcare%2C%20and%20nutrition.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20still%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20role%20of%20pregnancy%20and%20other%20aspects%20of%20reproduction%20in%20the%20aging%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unknown%20how%20rapid%20ageing%20will%20affect%20women's%20health%20and%20death%20as%20they%20grow%20old.%20%26quot%3BThe%20message%20here%20is%20not%20all%20doom%20and%20gloom%20-%20but%20it%20does%20highlight%20the%20fact%20that%20we've%20been%20so%20focused%20on%20outcomes%20for%20infants%20that%20we%20often%20forget%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20moms.%20Strong%20medical%2C%20social%20and%20nutritional%20support%20for%20new%20moms%20is%20always%20the%20best%20policy%20over%20the%20long%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ryan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20of%20the%20study%20have%20been%20published%20in%20the%20'Proceedings%20of%20National%20Academy%20of%20Sciences'.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712849040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fp4vjbm0g_pregnancy_625x300_11_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpregnancy-may-accelerate-biological-ageing-in-young-women-says-study-5421302%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20study's%20author%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BStrong%20medical%2C%20social%20and%20nutritional%20support%20for%20new%20moms%20is%20always%20the%20best%20policy%20over%20the%20long%20run%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpregnancy-may-accelerate-biological-ageing-in-young-women-says-study-5421302%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpregnancy-may-accelerate-biological-ageing-in-young-women-says-study-5421302%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpregnancy-may-accelerate-biological-ageing-in-young-women-says-study-5421302%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kishan%20Sledges%20Injured%20Faf%20As%20MI%20Pacer's%20Screamer%20Hits%20Him%20Hard.%20See%20Pics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Mumbai%20Indians%20vs%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20is%20a%20clash%20of%20titans%20in%20many%20sense.%20While%20there%20is%20no%20comparison%20in%20their%20trophy%20cabinet%2C%20with%20MI%20winning%20IPL%20five%20times%20while%20RCB%20yet%20to%20open%20the%20account%2C%20the%20teams%20are%20filled%20with%20stars.%20While%20MI%20have%20the%20likes%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspor