0thousands%20of%20Ukrainian%20men%20evade%20the%20draft.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraines-parliament-passes-a-controversial-law-to-boost-much-needed-conscripts-and-fill-army-ranks%2Farticleshow%2F109217858.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraines-parliament-passes-a-controversial-law-to-boost-much-needed-conscripts-and-fill-army-ranks%2Famp_articleshow%2F109217858.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraines-parliament-passes-a-controversial-law-to-boost-much-needed-conscripts-and-fill-army-ranks%2Famp_articleshow%2F109217858.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Live%20With%20Locals%20%26amp%3B%20Help%20Protect%20Snow%20Leopards%20at%20These%20Ladakh%20Homestays%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20morning%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20Deachen%20Chuksit%20went%20to%20her%20field%20to%20milk%20the%20cows%2C%20a%20usual%20morning%20routine.%20But%20she%20was%20distraught%20to%20find%20one%20missing.%20As%20a%20native%20of%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%94%20also%20home%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343873%2Fwildlife-photographer-naturalist-in-ladakh-karamjeet-singh-snow-leopards-himalayan-brown-bear-endangered-species%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnow%20leopard%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20this%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20as%20a%20shock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%E2%80%99d%20often%20heard%20of%20the%20snow%20leopard%E2%80%99s%20notoriety%20and%20how%20it%20ruthlessly%20killed%20her%20neighbour%E2%80%99s%20cattle%20and%20sheep%20as%20they%20innocently%20grazed%20on%20the%20mountain%20pastures.%20But%2C%20today%2C%20she%20was%20a%20victim%20of%20the%20same%20fate.%20Years%20ago%2C%20Deachen%E2%80%99s%20reaction%20to%20this%20horrifying%20incident%20would%20be%20to%20weep.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20she%20dialled%20a%20number%20on%20her%20phone%20and%20calmly%20narrated%20the%20loss%20she%20had%20just%20witnessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20person%20on%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20line%20was%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%20%E2%80%94%20the%20present%20director%20at%20the%20Snow%20Leopard%20Conservancy%20India%20Trust.%20Patiently%2C%20he%20heard%20Deachen%20out.%20The%20next%20month%2C%20an%20amount%20of%20Rs%207%2C000%20made%20its%20way%20to%20her.%20The%20money%20was%20a%20reimbursement%20for%20the%20cow%20she%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310452%2Fbengaluru-student-financial-independence-portal-for-domestic-workers-finwin-anaya-jethanandani%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einsurance%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Mr%20Namgail%20has%20started%20is%20very%20helpful%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tsewang%20Norboo%2C%20Deachen%E2%80%99s%20brother-in-law%20shares.%20He%20has%20been%20helping%20her%20out%20following%20the%20death%20of%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20every%20village%20home%20pays%20an%20annual%20sum%20of%20Rs%20400.%20The%20cumulative%20amount%20goes%20into%20the%20bank%20account%20that%20Namgail%20has%20set%20up.%20When%20a%20villager%20reports%20an%20incident%20of%20a%20missing%20cow%20or%20goat%2C%20citing%20the%20snow%20leopard%20as%20the%20culprit%2C%20they%20are%20compensated%20with%20Rs%205%2C000%20(for%20a%20small%20animal)%20and%20Rs%207%2C000%20(for%20a%20larger%20animal).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENamgail%20took%20over%20as%20director%20in%202013%2C%20after%20the%20passing%20away%20of%20his%20beloved%20friend%20and%20mentor%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk.%20The%20Ladakhi%20mountaineer%20and%20conservationist%20had%20co-founded%20the%20trust%20in%202003%20along%20with%20biologist%20Rodney%20Jackson%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20prioritising%20a%20harmonious%20relationship%20between%20the%20snow%20leopard%20and%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20return%20to%20the%20place%20he%20once%20called%20home%20is%20special%20for%20Namgail%20who%20was%20previously%20working%20as%20a%20wildlife%20biologist%20in%20the%20United%20States%20where%20he%20was%20studying%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F81077%2Fmigratory-birds-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emigratory%20patterns%20of%20birds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20always%20harboured%20a%20dream%20to%20come%20back%20to%20Ladakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20A%20burning%20desire%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20environmental%20and%20ecological%20issues%20was%20behind%20this%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20when%20in%202012%2C%20the%20trust%20seemed%20to%20be%20struggling%20after%20the%20passing%20away%20of%20its%20leader%2C%20Namgail%20knew%20it%20was%20time%20to%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy--1711367266.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Snow%20Leopard%20Conservancy%20India%20Trust%20is%20involved%20in%20the%20protection%20and%20conservation%20of%20snow%20leopards%20through%20tourism%2C%20research%2C%20photography%20and%20more%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy--1711367266.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy--1711367266-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy--1711367266-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%