und%20confidence.%20They%20no%20longer%20hate%20the%20feline.%20In%20fact%2C%20a%20major%20chunk%20of%20their%20incomes%20is%20generated%20by%20snow%20leopard-related%20tourism.%20To%20make%20up%20for%20the%20favour%2C%20the%20locals%20do%20not%20hunt%20the%20animals%20down%2C%20as%20they%20once%20did%2C%20thus%20allowing%20their%20population%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20spearheading%20this%20harmony%20between%20beast%20and%20man%20has%20been%20the%20conservancy.%20But%20credit%20Namgail%20for%20leading%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335727%2Fintach-bengaluru-convenor-meera-iyer-restoring-forgotten-heritage-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20unique%20endeavour%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20this%2C%20and%20he%20says%20he%20owes%20his%20success%20to%20Wangchuk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20before%20I%20took%20over%20as%20director%20in%202013%2C%20I%20remember%20accompanying%20Mr%20Rinchen%20to%20the%20villages%20of%20Ladakh%20and%20speaking%20to%20the%20locals.%20He%20was%20a%20great%20visionary.%20We%20would%20conduct%20numerous%20surveys%20to%20check%20on%20the%20mountain%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20lovely%20experience%20to%20learn%20from%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20had%20known%20each%20other%20for%20years.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20college%20days%2C%20I%20would%20lead%20the%20tourists%20into%20the%20mountains%20during%20the%20summer.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Mr%20Rinchen%20was%20working%20on%20some%20projects%20for%20the%20International%20Snow%20Leopard%20Trust%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20met%2C%E2%80%9D%20Namgail%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20so%20much%20to%20learn%20from%20Wangchuk%2C%20he%20says.%20In%20the%20years%20to%20come%2C%20a%20simple%20afternoon%20conversation%20between%20a%20young%20college%20boy%20and%20his%20idol%20blossomed%20into%20a%20beautiful%20friendship.%20Little%20did%20Na