n-and-where-to-see-the-next-total-solar-eclipse-13112212%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhen-and-where-to-see-the-next-total-solar-eclipse-13112212%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhen-and-where-to-see-the-next-total-solar-eclipse-13112212%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20This%20Man%20is%20a%20Messiah%20for%20Hundreds%20of%20Tribals%20Dying%20Due%20to%20Incurable%20Silicosis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mention%20of%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20morning%2C%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Parvati%20Mardi%20would%20comb%20her%20hair%2C%20wear%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebindi%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20set%20out%20to%20work%20in%20a%20clean%20saree.%20But%20by%20the%20evening%2C%20she%20would%20be%20beyond%20recognisable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20worked%20in%20a%20ramming%20mass%20industry.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20she%20would%20be%20exposed%20to%20silica%20dust%20all%20day.%20I%20remember%20that%20whenever%20she%20would%20come%20home%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20she%20would%20be%20completely%20covered%20in%20dust%20%E2%80%94%20her%20hair%2C%20clothes%2C%20all%20her%20body.%20It%20would%20get%20a%20little%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20recognise%20her.%20The%20first%20thing%20ma%20would%20do%20was%20to%20take%20a%20bath%20before%20touching%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20daughter%20Laxmi%20Mardi%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20tribal%20belts%20of%20Jharkhand%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20workers%20are%20forced%20to%20work%20in%20the%20ramming%20mass%20factories%20where%20quartzite%20stones%20are%20ground%20and%20powdered%20into%20dust%20and%20different-sized%20particles%20to%20prepare%20%E2%80%98ramming%20mass%E2%80%99.%20This%20is%20used%20to%20produce%20refractory%20items%20like%20fire%20bricks%20for%20steel%20industries%20and%20to%20manufacture%20insulators%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F191127%2Fdelhi-boy-innovation-recycling-glass-bottle-sand-construction-green-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esilica%20sand%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20huge%20quartzite%20stones%20are%20broken%20and%20milled%2C%20dust%20is%20released.%20This%20dust%20contains%20silicon%20dioxide%20which%20when%20inhaled%20over%20some%20time%20leads%20to%20silicosis%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20noticing%20that%20our%20mother%20would%20cough%20a%20lot%20and%20often%20complained%20about%20facing%20difficulty%20in%20breathing.%20Day%20by%20day%2C%20she%20also%20started%20losing%20weight%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20continued%20for%20four%20years%20until%20one%20day%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20in%20April%202012.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20first%20time%20we%20heard%20about%20the%20disease.%20We%20took%20her%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20but%20we%20were%20too%20young%20to%20understand%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20disease%20and%20how%20long%20she%20was%20going%20to%20stay%20with%20us.%20I%20was%2014%20years%20old%20then%2C%20and%20I%20was%20told%20that%20she%20would%20be%20home%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Parvati%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20silicosis%20in%202012.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20she%20lost%20her%20succumbed%20to%20the%20disease.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.t