20the%20rights%20of%20tribal%20workers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20there%20has%20been%20immense%20politics%20right%20from%20the%20hospital%20level%20to%20the%20state%20officials.%20Many%20times%2C%20doctors%20also%20refuse%20to%20write%20correct%20reports%20because%20of%20pressure%20from%20higher%20authorities.%20We%20keep%20making%20rounds%20of%20the%20officials%20at%20the%20district%20levels%20to%20get%20these%20families%20their%20compensation%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20knocking%20on%20several%20official%20doors%2C%20Samit%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20(NHRC)%20and%20filed%20a%20petition%20on%208%20October%2C%202007%2C%20to%20seek%20their%20support%20for%20the%20relief%20of%20silicosis%20patients%20and%20their%20families.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20amount%20of%20allocation%2C%20it%20directs%20the%20Government%20to%20provide%20Rs%204%20lakh%20compensation%20to%20the%20kin%20of%20dead%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20Samit%20says%2C%20his%20organisation%20was%20able%20to%20source%20compensation%20amounts%20worth%20Rs%2013.52%20crore%20for%20workers%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20were%20able%20to%20raise%20Rs%2088%20lakh%20from%20donors%20in%2010%20years%20in%20both%20states%20for%20the%20treatment%20of%20silicosis%20patients%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamit%20says%20that%20the%20monetary%20support%20from%20the%20Government%20is%20extremely%20important%20for%20these%20families.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20breadwinners%20of%20the%20families%20die%2C%20young%20orphan%20children%20are%20forced%20to%20migrate%20for%20earning%20opportunities%20and%20lose%20their%20right%20to%20education.%20For%20them%2C%20the%20monetary%20compensation%20is%20a%20ray%20of%20hope%20for%20a%20better%20future.%20Many%20families%20have%20used%20these%20amounts%20to%20set%20up%20small%20businesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20children%20but%20whenever%20I%20see%20young%20kids%20of%20dead%20workers%2C%20it%20aches%20my%20heart.%20Thankfully%2C%20with%20our%20small%20efforts%2C%20we%20can%20protect%20the%20future%20generations%20of%20some%20such%20workers.%20Now%20as%20I%20am%20getting%20old%2C%20I%20want%20to%20pass%20on%20my%20experience%20to%20dedicated%20people%20so%20that%20this%20work%20does%20not%20stop%20even%20after%20me.%20Otherwise%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20organisation%20by%202025.%20We%20also%20require%20decent%20funding%20support%20to%20continue%20this%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Samit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20support%20him%20in%20his%20mission%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20Samit%20Kumar%20Carr%20at%20roshniforlabour%40gmail.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fsociety%2Ftheres-a-scourge-of-silicosis-among-mine-and-factory-workers-in-jharkhand%2Farticle65092384.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBreathless%3A%20Silicosis%20is%20killing%20workers%20in%20Jharkhand%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3EBy%20Vikram%20Raj%20for%20The%20Hindu%20published%20on%204%20March%202022.%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Samit%20Kumar%20Carr.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712749731000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsilicosis-1711118788.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20Jharkhand's%20Samit%20Kumar%20Carr%20has%20helped%20families%20of%20workers%20who%20died%20due%20to%20incurable%20silicosis%20get%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%2013%2