0casing%20and%20function%20like%20open%20recharge%20wells.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWherever%20we%20do%20good%20%5Bopen%5D%20recharge%20%5Bwells%5D%20and%20lakes%20are%20revived%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20shallow%20aquifer%20which%20comes%20back%20to%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FeXn1Lx725Js%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FeXn1Lx725Js%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%20believes%20that%20every%20building%20in%20Bengaluru%20can%20be%20part%20of%20the%20solution.%20%E2%80%9CTake%20all%20the%20rainwater%20you%20can%2C%20store%20it%20in%20a%20sump%20tank%20and%20reuse%20it.%20If%20you%20have%20excess%20rainwater%2C%20please%20make%20sure%20that%20this%20goes%20into%20recharge%20wells%20so%20that%20the%20shallow%20aquifer%20is%20full%20and%20then%20you%20dip%20into%20it%20in%20times%20of%20need.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20overall%20goal%20of%20our%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173853%2Fbengaluru-ground-water-crisis-well-digging-day-zero-zenrainman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%