b007c08f9e7a99%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Frei-fired-manager-union-campaign_n_660b0c31e4b007c08f9e7a99%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%20is%20Empowering%202500%20Indian%20Women%20Scale%20Their%20Micro%20Enterprises%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20published%20in%20partnership%20with%20I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20India%20has%20been%20a%20witness%20to%20innovation%20and%20entrepreneurship%20taking%20centre%20stage.%20The%20Economic%20Survey%20of%202023%20highlights%20a%20surge%20in%20entrepreneurship%20which%20is%20not%20only%20setting%20a%20precedent%20for%20the%20future%20generations%20but%20changing%20the%20concept%20of%20employment.%20The%20report%20also%20indicates%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345161%2Ftvaran-by-cisco-villgro-empower-women-led-startups-female-entrepreneurs-climate-action%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estartup%20ecosystem%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20will%20create%20over%2010%20lakh%20jobs%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20Indian%20School%20of%20Business%20(ISB)%2C%20through%20their%20one-of-a-kind%20%E2%80%98I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20programme%20is%20providing%20the%20required%20support%20to%20this%20ecosystem%20and%20championing%20entrepreneurship%20for%20every%20section%20of%20the%20society%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20its%20purview%2C%20there%20are%20various%20programmes%20all%20fostering%20entrepreneurship%20and%20nurturing%20startups%20by%20providing%20them%20with%20%E2%80%98Start-to-Scale%E2%80%99%20support%20that%20will%20accelerate%20their%20conversion%20into%20profitable%20ventures.%20One%20such%20recently%20launched%20programme%20%E2%80%98DiscoverShe%E2%80%99%2C%20brings%20together%20the%20goals%20of%20a%20profitable%20venture%20while%20upholding%20the%20inclusion%20of%20w